{"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"linkSpacePaddingInline","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SpaceSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena"}],"title":"linkSpacePaddingInline","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC22linkSpacePaddingInlineSdvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.spacePaddingInlineNone","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"linkSpacePaddingInline","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/linkSpacePaddingInline","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/linkspacepaddinginline"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Link","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/linkSpacePaddingInline":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"linkSpacePaddingInline"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"linkSpacePaddingInline","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/linkSpacePaddingInline","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/linkspacepaddinginline","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token spaces.spacePaddingInlineNone","type":"text"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"}}}